            "paragraph": "For Brisha Rashi, Today asks you to protect peace around you. Focus on money, food, family, and steady work. Home and close relations can feel better with gentle behavior. Give time to rest, food, and small family duties. Avoid taking every small word personally. Your lucky color is green and your lucky number is 9.",
